hadithonline\/2012\/09\/19\/slaves-equal-treament\/","url_meta":{"origin":6670,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Equality: Slaves are equals in food, clothing, dignity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Ma\u2019rur ibn Suwayd reported: I met Abu Dharr while he was wearing the same clothes as his servant boy. I asked him about it, and he said, \"I once abused a man and insulted his mother, so the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to me, 'O Abu\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26246,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/04\/23\/slaves-servants-do-not-torture\/","url_meta":{"origin":6670,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Slaves: Do not torture slaves, whom Allah created","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is suitable for you among your slaves,\u00a0 feed them from the same food you eat and clothe them from the same clothes you wear. Whoever is not suitable for you, sell them and do not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10056,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/26\/prophet-good-treatment-slaves\/","url_meta":{"origin":6670,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Slaves: The Prophet orders good treatment of slaves","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 26, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, enjoined good treatment of slaves and he would say, \u201cFeed them from the same food you eat, clothe them from the same clothes you wear, and do not torture the creation of Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 188\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10098,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/01\/prophet-never-hit-women\/","url_meta":{"origin":6670,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Beatings: The Prophet never hit women, servants, animals","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, never struck anything with his hand, neither a woman nor a servant, unless he was fighting in the way of Allah. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2328 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim Imam al-Nawawi commented, \u201cStriking a wife, a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23219,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/14\/no-dua-against-family-community\/","url_meta":{"origin":6670,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Do not supplicate against yourself, your community","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not supplicate against yourselves, do not supplicate against your children, and do not supplicate against your wealth, lest it coincide with a time in which Allah is asked and he gives and your supplication\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1046,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/10\/04\/servants-allah-brothers-sisters\/","url_meta":{"origin":6670,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ikhwah: Be servants of Allah as brothers and sisters","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not hate each other, do not envy each other, do not turn away from each other, but rather be servants of Allah as brothers. It is not lawful for a Muslim to boycott\u00a0his brother\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6670","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6670"}],"versi